{"id":93,"count":1,"description":"Divine Uttar Pradesh \u2013 A spiritual heartland of India, Uttar Pradesh is home to some of the country\u2019s most sacred and historic sites. From the holy city of Varanasi, where the Ganga Aarti lights up the ghats, to Ayodhya, the birthplace of Lord Rama, and Prayagraj, where the sacred confluence of Ganga, Yamuna, and Saraswati hosts the grand Kumbh Mela, the state is steeped in devotion. Add to this the architectural marvels of Mathura and Vrindavan, the land of Lord Krishna, and the timeless heritage of magnificent forts and temples, and you get a destination that beautifully blends spirituality, culture, and history. Uttar Pradesh is truly where divinity meets tradition.","link":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/destinations\/devine-uttarpradesh\/","name":"DEVINE UTTARPRADESH","slug":"devine-uttarpradesh","taxonomy":"destination","parent":0,"meta":[],"thumbnail":{"width":900,"height":596,"file":"2025\/09\/DEVINE-UTTARPRADESH.png","filesize":907780,"sizes":{"medium":{"file":"DEVINE-UTTARPRADESH-300x199.png","width":300,"height":199,"filesize":85283,"mime_type":"image\/png","source_url":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/DEVINE-UTTARPRADESH-300x199.png"},"thumbnail":{"file":"DEVINE-UTTARPRADESH-150x150.png","width":150,"height":150,"filesize":35732,"mime_type":"image\/png","source_url":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/DEVINE-UTTARPRADESH-150x150.png"},"medium_large":{"file":"DEVINE-UTTARPRADESH-768x509.png","width":768,"height":509,"filesize":431727,"mime_type":"image\/png","source_url":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/DEVINE-UTTARPRADESH-768x509.png"},"trip-thumb-size":{"file":"DEVINE-UTTARPRADESH-374x226.png","width":374,"height":226,"filesize":116571,"mime_type":"image\/png","source_url":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/DEVINE-UTTARPRADESH-374x226.png"},"destination-thumb-siz